WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.900
=Episode 18=

01:38.020 --> 01:40.380
If the man in black
is truly the mastermind,

01:41.900 --> 01:43.770
perhaps I might spare you.

01:44.290 --> 01:45.410
He won't speak, but I'll.

01:47.850 --> 01:49.330
The first time I saw the man in black

01:49.740 --> 01:51.490
was not long after Nie Zhe
became the Chief.

01:51.690 --> 01:53.180
Many in the sect refused to submit.

01:55.980 --> 01:57.210
Kill those people,

01:57.770 --> 02:00.020
and you can secure your position.

02:07.740 --> 02:09.596
With the man in black's help,

02:09.607 --> 02:10.769
Nie Zhe eliminated dissenters

02:10.780 --> 02:12.050
and gradually secured his power.

02:12.340 --> 02:13.500
From then on,

02:13.500 --> 02:15.500
he obeyed the man
in black without question.

02:16.290 --> 02:19.010
The man in black also gave him
Suzi Fragrance and Qianxun Wood.

02:19.890 --> 02:21.340
Nie Zhe then forced me

02:21.780 --> 02:22.940
to use the Suzi Fragrance

02:23.260 --> 02:24.690
to poison your father.

02:25.130 --> 02:26.940
Who exactly is the man in black?

02:27.380 --> 02:28.220
That person

02:29.100 --> 02:30.730
has never shown his true face.

02:31.220 --> 02:32.060
Oh, right.

02:32.340 --> 02:35.260
He also revealed Yin Dai's whereabouts.

02:35.260 --> 02:37.540
That was how Nie Zhe had
the chance to kill Yin Dai

02:37.540 --> 02:39.290
and avenge the former chief.

02:39.290 --> 02:41.130
Even I can't find him.

02:41.130 --> 02:43.260
You'll never be able to find him.

02:43.260 --> 02:45.890
You'll never avenge your father.

02:46.170 --> 02:47.010
Take him away.

02:52.730 --> 02:53.570
Qingyan,

02:54.500 --> 02:56.500
I have told you everything.

02:57.610 --> 02:59.220
Can you spare me now?

03:03.060 --> 03:04.220
I'll spare you.

03:06.820 --> 03:08.500
I'll also leave you here

03:08.500 --> 03:09.380
alone

03:10.940 --> 03:12.340
to die of old age.

03:12.660 --> 03:13.400
Qingyan.

03:13.500 --> 03:14.380
Qingyan.

03:14.730 --> 03:15.780
Qingyan!

03:16.010 --> 03:18.660
I know I was wrong.

03:18.660 --> 03:20.410
Please forgive me.

03:20.410 --> 03:21.690
Qingyan!

03:25.500 --> 03:27.100
Don't believe Nie Zhe.

03:28.610 --> 03:30.540
The man in black supported him
for so many years.

03:30.980 --> 03:32.170
He'll surely come to save him.

03:32.850 --> 03:34.220
We'll wait here.

03:34.410 --> 03:35.570
We'll definitely catch him.

04:05.380 --> 04:06.500
He still hasn't come?

04:07.820 --> 04:10.100
Has Nie Zhe become a discarded pawn?

04:10.100 --> 04:11.660
He has schemed for so long.

04:12.410 --> 04:13.980
He won't give up so easily.

04:13.980 --> 04:14.980
I'm exhausted.

04:14.980 --> 04:15.820
We'll wait slowly.

04:54.730 --> 04:55.610
Young Master...

05:01.020 --> 05:01.860
What is it?

05:02.196 --> 05:03.850
The Jade Sunflower
isn't in the treasury.

05:03.850 --> 05:04.690
It has been stolen.

05:12.050 --> 05:12.890
Lu Chengnan?

05:15.140 --> 05:17.540
Isn't he Nie Hengcheng's most trusted

05:17.540 --> 05:19.290
and most valued disciple?

05:20.100 --> 05:21.780
Why would he steal the Jade Sunflower?

05:21.780 --> 05:23.490
No idea.

05:23.490 --> 05:25.340
After Nie Hengcheng discovered it,

05:25.340 --> 05:26.730
he was furious

05:26.730 --> 05:28.340
and injured Lu Chengnan.

05:28.340 --> 05:30.170
I was there at the time.

05:30.170 --> 05:32.610
Nie Hengcheng was like a madman,

05:32.610 --> 05:33.980
striking without restraint.

05:33.980 --> 05:35.730
He meant to kill him.

05:35.730 --> 05:39.020
When Han Yisu saw
Nie Hengcheng's intent to kill,

05:39.020 --> 05:41.980
he desperately tried to stop him

05:41.980 --> 05:44.780
while shouting for Lu Chengnan to run.

05:45.580 --> 05:46.540
I haven't seen

05:46.540 --> 05:48.410
Lu Chengnan since.

05:49.370 --> 05:52.220
The Jade Sunflower is also missing.

05:52.220 --> 05:53.780
This Jade Sunflower

05:53.780 --> 05:55.810
is merely a healing item

05:55.810 --> 05:57.930
to calm the mind and warm the meridians.

05:57.930 --> 05:59.850
Why would Nie Hengcheng value it so much

06:00.540 --> 06:02.980
that he'd injure his trusted disciple?

06:02.980 --> 06:05.980
Lu Chengnan was even the next chief.

06:06.410 --> 06:09.900
Why offend Nie Hengcheng
over a mere object?

06:11.140 --> 06:12.140
Young Master,

06:12.140 --> 06:14.340
our treasury holds so many treasures.

06:14.730 --> 06:16.610
Why did you ask specifically

06:16.610 --> 06:18.340
about the Jade Sunflower?

06:20.660 --> 06:21.500
To repay a favor.

06:24.700 --> 06:27.220
The Wanzai Stone beneath Mount Lieyan?

06:28.700 --> 06:30.700
Though it can't eradicate
the Nether Aura,

06:31.370 --> 06:33.220
its effect of warming the meridians

06:33.220 --> 06:34.370
is exceptional.

06:35.170 --> 06:37.170
I hope you won't disdain it

06:37.170 --> 06:38.250
and accept it.

06:41.177 --> 06:43.250
The chaos caused by Nie Zhe
has yet to be resolved.

06:43.410 --> 06:44.730
The Jade Sunflower

06:44.730 --> 06:46.810
may have fallen elsewhere.

06:46.810 --> 06:48.660
If I find it one day,

06:48.660 --> 06:50.540
I'll immediately deliver it to you.

06:51.170 --> 06:52.010
Thanks.

06:55.340 --> 06:56.810
Since you've found this,

06:57.660 --> 06:59.660
you should return early to recuperate.

07:00.170 --> 07:01.010
How about this?

07:01.580 --> 07:02.700
Tomorrow morning,

07:02.700 --> 07:04.660
I'll send someone to escort you out.

07:07.700 --> 07:09.020
Will Zhao leave with me?

07:11.850 --> 07:13.036
She has matters to attend to,

07:13.730 --> 07:15.540
so she won't leave with you.

07:16.020 --> 07:17.340
Do you still remember

07:18.220 --> 07:20.340
what we said about following
the natural course?

07:20.780 --> 07:22.220
During this trip,

07:22.220 --> 07:24.540
I witnessed Nie Zhe's cruelty.

07:24.540 --> 07:26.930
I now know the rumors
about Li Sect are not false.

07:27.580 --> 07:28.900
Our feud runs deep.

07:29.340 --> 07:31.340
Centuries of blood debts and division

07:31.340 --> 07:33.220
can't be resolved in a single day.

07:34.580 --> 07:35.810
Speak plainly.

07:37.660 --> 07:39.220
Zhao won't stay.

07:39.730 --> 07:41.220
The overall situation here is settled.

07:41.220 --> 07:42.220
In a few days,

07:42.810 --> 07:44.410
we'll return.

07:57.340 --> 07:59.850
This mountain map is so detailed.

08:00.220 --> 08:01.660
Since you wanted to see it,

08:01.660 --> 08:03.700
I asked them for the most complete copy.

08:05.780 --> 08:07.220
Miss Cai,

08:07.220 --> 08:09.100
are we still waiting here tonight?

08:10.140 --> 08:11.170
Of course.

08:11.580 --> 08:13.100
If we don't catch the culprit,

08:13.100 --> 08:15.290
how can we console Uncle Chang's spirit?

08:15.580 --> 08:17.220
If that person never comes,

08:17.540 --> 08:19.410
will you keep waiting?

08:26.113 --> 08:27.952
(Starry Terrace, Sandy Ridge)
How vast.

08:27.963 --> 08:30.648
No wonder the mountains have sustained
Li Sect for over 200 years.

08:30.659 --> 08:31.850
Naturally.

08:31.850 --> 08:33.530
Our mountains have always been rich

08:33.530 --> 08:34.883
in resources and self-sufficient.

08:35.130 --> 08:36.580
I heard from my grandfather

08:36.580 --> 08:39.370
that before the former chief went mad,

08:39.370 --> 08:41.340
Li Sect lived very well.

08:41.340 --> 08:43.370
There were markets, shops,

08:43.370 --> 08:44.730
workshops, and eateries.

08:44.730 --> 08:46.580
Life was peaceful and harmonious.

08:47.300 --> 08:49.610
But it declined later.

08:49.610 --> 08:51.530
Especially after Nie Zhe took office,

08:51.530 --> 08:53.650
people suffered,
and resentment filled the air.

08:54.868 --> 08:57.268
But now, the Young Master
has taken charge of Bliss Palace.

08:57.279 --> 08:59.039
The Li Sect will soon prosper again.

09:01.490 --> 09:03.610
He'll surely be a good chief.

09:03.610 --> 09:04.980
Grandfather is returning soon.

09:04.980 --> 09:06.850
I must go back to the village
to tidy up.

09:07.850 --> 09:09.530
He'll be back so soon?

09:09.530 --> 09:10.890
Is it unpleasant outside?

09:10.890 --> 09:12.820
A few days outside is fine.

09:12.820 --> 09:14.340
Too long won't do.

09:14.340 --> 09:15.890
People outside the mountains

09:15.890 --> 09:17.610
don't truly accept us.

09:18.130 --> 09:19.420
It is better to return home.

09:20.700 --> 09:21.770
Miss Cai,

09:23.220 --> 09:24.850
will you also return home?

09:29.010 --> 09:30.250
It is time to go back.

09:30.250 --> 09:31.700
Otherwise, my family will worry.

09:31.700 --> 09:33.100
If you return, the Young Master...

09:34.420 --> 09:35.820
Greetings, Young Master.

09:35.820 --> 09:37.180
I'll take my leave first.

09:40.700 --> 09:41.540
You're here.

09:49.790 --> 09:51.450
Do you want to go
to the Hanhai Mountains?

10:05.610 --> 10:08.130
The Hanhai Mountains are so beautiful.

10:08.130 --> 10:09.010
Yet this was the place

10:09.610 --> 10:11.730
my father most wished to leave.

10:12.530 --> 10:13.610
Why?

10:13.610 --> 10:15.250
My father once said,

10:15.250 --> 10:17.650
"The Mu clan has governed Li Sect
for 200 years."

10:17.650 --> 10:19.650
"Every child born into the Mu clan"

10:19.650 --> 10:21.092
"must study diligently without rest,"

10:21.103 --> 10:22.300
"resist the Six Sects,"

10:23.340 --> 10:25.130
"and control the unruly subordinates."

10:25.130 --> 10:27.060
"Their entire lives are trapped here."

10:27.940 --> 10:28.780
"It is enough."

10:29.130 --> 10:30.650
Then why did he not leave?

10:31.010 --> 10:32.820
Because Elder Qiu begged him bitterly.

10:33.420 --> 10:34.340
Elder Qiu said

10:36.420 --> 10:37.820
that if my father left,

10:38.940 --> 10:41.490
Nie Hengcheng would act
without restraint.

10:41.490 --> 10:43.250
Those loyal to the Mu clan

10:44.060 --> 10:45.490
would be slaughtered.

10:46.650 --> 10:47.490
He could not bear it,

10:47.980 --> 10:49.100
so he stayed.

10:49.770 --> 10:51.580
Later, he met Sun Ruoshui

10:52.530 --> 10:54.010
and had me.

10:54.010 --> 10:55.730
In my childhood, I suffered greatly,

10:55.730 --> 10:57.490
barely clinging to life.

10:57.490 --> 10:59.130
So, he stayed again.

11:00.180 --> 11:01.490
Until two years ago,

11:03.610 --> 11:05.300
he was poisoned by Sun Ruoshui.

11:05.300 --> 11:06.490
Not long after,

11:07.940 --> 11:09.180
he passed away.

11:09.610 --> 11:12.220
So, he never managed to leave.

11:14.130 --> 11:15.220
Mu Qingyan!

11:36.299 --> 11:38.185
The poison has spread
to your limbs and organs.

11:38.610 --> 11:39.530
It can't be suppressed.

11:40.700 --> 11:42.420
Why has it suddenly worsened like this?

11:42.940 --> 11:44.650
Suzi Fragrance has no cure.

11:46.100 --> 11:47.010
Perhaps

11:49.010 --> 11:50.220
the time has come.

11:53.820 --> 11:55.010
I'll find someone to save you.

12:00.340 --> 12:02.220
Even Uncle Lei is helpless.

12:04.300 --> 12:05.340
In this vast world,

12:06.340 --> 12:07.530
who else can you find?

12:15.580 --> 12:16.420
Zhao,

12:18.340 --> 12:20.300
I still have one unfulfilled wish.

12:21.820 --> 12:23.220
Are you willing to help me?

12:23.650 --> 12:24.530
What is it?

12:27.940 --> 12:29.940
In these final days,

12:32.420 --> 12:34.650
I hope you can stay by my side.

12:48.490 --> 12:49.330
After all,

12:50.700 --> 12:52.220
in my current state,

12:53.730 --> 12:55.340
I won't delay you for long.

12:57.980 --> 12:58.820
All right.

13:00.300 --> 13:01.220
I'll stay with you.

13:21.940 --> 13:24.500
(Carefree)

14:18.100 --> 14:18.940
Young Master,

14:19.770 --> 14:20.610
your health...

14:21.130 --> 14:22.130
Say no more.

14:59.850 --> 15:00.850
Yuzhi.

15:04.580 --> 15:05.420
Zhao,

15:06.610 --> 15:08.060
when do you plan to return?

15:11.980 --> 15:13.420
In a few more days.

15:13.420 --> 15:15.460
I've received a pigeon message
from Guangtian Gate.

15:15.770 --> 15:17.940
Master and the others
are already outside.

15:18.420 --> 15:19.490
If we don't return soon,

15:19.490 --> 15:20.700
they might force their way in.

15:21.130 --> 15:22.220
Zhao, have you considered

15:23.490 --> 15:24.850
how this will end?

15:25.490 --> 15:27.300
You may leave on your own.

15:31.420 --> 15:32.610
Why did you come out?

15:32.610 --> 15:33.490
It's windy outside.

15:33.490 --> 15:34.770
Hurry back and lie down.

15:35.580 --> 15:36.420
I'm fine.

15:39.180 --> 15:40.020
Yuzhi,

15:41.700 --> 15:42.890
just give me a few more days.

15:47.420 --> 15:48.340
Go back now.

16:01.980 --> 16:02.940
Thank you, Uncle Cheng.

16:04.420 --> 16:06.180
You even prepared Smiley for me.

16:07.370 --> 16:08.300
Open your mouth.

16:08.300 --> 16:09.140
Young Master.

16:15.650 --> 16:16.490
You...

16:19.770 --> 16:20.610
Young Master,

16:21.100 --> 16:23.180
are you going to repeat
the Mu clan's past mistakes?

16:23.180 --> 16:25.020
It seems Elder Yan has
something to say to me.

16:25.700 --> 16:26.540
Zhao,

16:26.980 --> 16:28.220
wait outside for me.

16:36.890 --> 16:37.850
Young Master,

16:38.130 --> 16:39.580
the marriages of your family

16:39.890 --> 16:41.490
have never

16:41.490 --> 16:43.130
ended well.

16:43.530 --> 16:45.940
The Young Lord suffered deeply.

16:45.940 --> 16:48.100
Why must you repeat the same mistake?

16:48.100 --> 16:50.060
You've only been released
for a few days.

16:51.370 --> 16:53.730
Do you wish to be locked back
in the Jiuzhou Archive?

16:54.490 --> 16:56.010
You can even throw me into the dungeon.

16:56.770 --> 16:58.420
Today, I must speak my mind.

16:58.730 --> 17:01.130
The Li Sect now stands amid ruins.

17:01.770 --> 17:04.570
This is your opportunity
to accomplish something.

17:04.570 --> 17:05.410
And now?

17:05.420 --> 17:07.010
For Miss Cai,

17:07.010 --> 17:09.140
you linger
in the Carefree Chamber all day,

17:09.140 --> 17:10.530
lost in warmth and comfort,

17:10.530 --> 17:11.940
neglecting progress.

17:11.940 --> 17:13.380
Do you wish to doom Li Sect?

17:13.770 --> 17:15.010
My father's dying wish

17:15.570 --> 17:16.810
was to dissolve Li Sect

17:17.380 --> 17:18.700
and leave the Hanhai Mountains.

17:18.700 --> 17:19.540
Perhaps

17:20.290 --> 17:21.583
I should issue the order at once

17:21.980 --> 17:23.770
and let the members depart freely.

17:24.220 --> 17:25.530
Would that not satisfy all?

17:26.900 --> 17:27.860
Young Master,

17:32.050 --> 17:33.420
forgive my bluntness.

17:34.660 --> 17:36.090
The one who killed the Young Lord

17:36.090 --> 17:37.180
was not Nie Zhe,

17:37.180 --> 17:38.620
nor Sun Ruoshui,

17:38.620 --> 17:40.530
but his merciful heart.

17:40.530 --> 17:42.050
His mercy

17:42.050 --> 17:43.010
could not even

17:43.660 --> 17:44.810
protect himself.

17:45.250 --> 17:46.090
Young Master,

17:46.420 --> 17:48.140
don't repeat the same mistake.

17:48.140 --> 17:49.050
Elder Yan,

17:50.810 --> 17:51.810
what a man my father was

17:52.700 --> 17:54.420
isn't for you to judge.

17:56.530 --> 17:57.940
I don't care who he was.

17:58.220 --> 17:59.420
He was a Mu.

18:00.090 --> 18:01.810
A Mu

18:01.810 --> 18:03.570
can't think only of themselves.

18:04.010 --> 18:05.810
For all the sect members,

18:05.810 --> 18:07.770
this is their home.

18:07.770 --> 18:09.220
If Li Sect prospers,

18:09.220 --> 18:10.660
we live and work in peace.

18:11.090 --> 18:13.050
If Li Sect is gone,

18:13.050 --> 18:14.090
we lose our home

18:14.090 --> 18:15.290
and suffer humiliation.

18:17.770 --> 18:18.610
Young Master,

18:18.770 --> 18:20.940
if you insist on going your own way,

18:20.940 --> 18:22.570
I'll release Nie Zhe at once

18:22.570 --> 18:23.730
and restore him as the Chief.

18:23.730 --> 18:25.290
Even if he acts tyrannically again,

18:25.290 --> 18:27.490
at least he can protect

18:27.490 --> 18:29.490
this ancestral foundation
for the sec members.

18:34.620 --> 18:35.460
It seems you

18:37.099 --> 18:38.605
truly have my best interests at heart.

18:40.250 --> 18:41.090
Young Master,

18:41.570 --> 18:43.220
please correct your actions now.

18:43.660 --> 18:44.770
But if I did not do this,

18:46.380 --> 18:48.860
how could I lure out Nie Zhe's remnants

18:49.940 --> 18:51.250
and wipe them out in one sweep?

19:02.380 --> 19:04.246
Once most of Nie Zhe's followers
are captured,

19:04.980 --> 19:06.730
Mr. Mu should recover, right?

19:07.860 --> 19:09.273
His chronic illness is hard to cure.

19:09.493 --> 19:10.490
He won't recover so soon.

19:10.700 --> 19:12.010
If it were truly that serious,

19:12.700 --> 19:14.980
would you and You
hunt down rebels everywhere?

19:17.710 --> 19:19.078
It's just a plan to lure the enemy

19:19.089 --> 19:19.900
and stall for time,

19:19.900 --> 19:21.530
killing two birds with one stone.

19:23.700 --> 19:24.540
Don't worry.

19:25.330 --> 19:27.180
This is your internal matter.

19:27.180 --> 19:28.020
I won't interfere.

19:29.810 --> 19:30.849
As for Miss Cai...

19:30.860 --> 19:32.309
She's involved too deeply to see it.

19:32.810 --> 19:34.290
No matter what others say,

19:34.290 --> 19:36.140
she should see through the maze herself.

19:36.940 --> 19:38.090
Zhao is intelligent.

19:38.090 --> 19:39.290
She'll see it on her own.

19:39.860 --> 19:41.770
Before that, I won't say another word.

19:42.620 --> 19:43.460
What a pity

19:44.090 --> 19:45.810
that you're from the Six Sects.

19:46.090 --> 19:47.180
In the future, we may gain

19:47.860 --> 19:49.220
another formidable enemy.

20:13.236 --> 20:15.010
She can't even swallow
her medicine anymore.

20:15.010 --> 20:15.850
Mother,

20:16.730 --> 20:18.330
is Aunt going to die?

20:31.880 --> 20:32.730
Aunt,

20:32.730 --> 20:33.570
take the medicine.

20:40.250 --> 20:41.090
Aunt!

20:51.250 --> 20:52.090
Qi,

20:53.380 --> 20:54.220
Pingshu

20:55.490 --> 20:56.860
is gone.

20:58.730 --> 20:59.770
Qi,

21:00.140 --> 21:00.980
don't be like this.

21:01.380 --> 21:02.770
Qi, don't be like this.

21:02.770 --> 21:03.610
Qi...

21:08.730 --> 21:09.570
Qi!

21:10.140 --> 21:11.050
Pingshu.

21:13.530 --> 21:14.420
Pingshu!

21:14.420 --> 21:16.420
She's gone. Qi, don't be like this.

21:16.420 --> 21:18.250
- Qi!
- Pingshu!

21:18.250 --> 21:19.900
Don't be like this, Qi!

21:19.900 --> 21:20.810
Pingshu!

21:25.090 --> 21:26.770
Why must they die?

21:31.530 --> 21:33.490
Why can't I do anything?

22:06.220 --> 22:07.060
Mu Qingyan.

22:19.330 --> 22:20.170
Zhao,

22:21.050 --> 22:21.890
you are here.

22:22.620 --> 22:23.810
Yan Xu is too rigid.

22:24.220 --> 22:25.490
I've driven him away.

22:26.250 --> 22:27.900
He won't disturb us again.

22:31.220 --> 22:32.060
Zhao,

22:33.490 --> 22:34.330
what is wrong?

22:35.140 --> 22:36.620
I've left the sect without permission

22:36.940 --> 22:38.380
for over two months.

22:39.180 --> 22:40.730
It's time for me to return.

22:42.530 --> 22:43.530
Today,

22:43.860 --> 22:45.090
I came to say goodbye.

22:45.810 --> 22:46.730
What did you say?

22:47.660 --> 22:49.050
I said I'm leaving.

22:49.050 --> 22:50.330
I'm returning to Qingque Sect.

22:50.810 --> 22:52.090
This is the demonic sect.

22:52.090 --> 22:53.980
I'm a disciple of the Six Sects.

22:53.980 --> 22:55.530
You've become the Chief.

22:56.250 --> 22:57.730
I can't stay any longer.

22:58.290 --> 22:59.420
But you promised me

23:01.380 --> 23:02.700
to stay with me.

23:05.180 --> 23:06.220
For how long?

23:09.900 --> 23:10.740
One year?

23:13.860 --> 23:14.810
Five years?

23:17.980 --> 23:19.220
Or ten years?

23:22.810 --> 23:23.860
You need not worry.

23:25.090 --> 23:26.530
This poison won't take that long.

23:31.570 --> 23:33.140
That may not be so.

23:34.660 --> 23:36.730
You're blessed with talent.

23:36.730 --> 23:38.090
Would mere Suzi Fragrance

23:38.090 --> 23:39.770
truly defeat you?

23:39.770 --> 23:40.940
What are you talking about?

23:49.980 --> 23:51.660
What clever tactics.

23:52.220 --> 23:54.660
Using the more potent Xungu Grass

23:54.660 --> 23:56.220
to trigger a new poison.

23:56.220 --> 23:58.570
It suppresses
the outbreak of Suzi Fragrance

23:58.570 --> 23:59.810
and lets you stage a fine act

23:59.810 --> 24:01.140
of being near death before me.

24:01.860 --> 24:03.220
How ruthless.

24:04.250 --> 24:05.090
Zhao,

24:06.490 --> 24:07.330
I...

24:09.700 --> 24:10.540
No.

24:12.770 --> 24:14.290
You didn't act for me.

24:14.980 --> 24:17.900
You acted for the whole world.

24:18.620 --> 24:19.770
I was wondering

24:20.730 --> 24:22.180
why, with your poison flaring,

24:22.900 --> 24:24.620
Shangguan Haonan and You Guanyue

24:24.620 --> 24:26.290
were nowhere to be seen.

24:26.290 --> 24:27.490
Now, I understand.

24:28.290 --> 24:30.330
They are busy capturing
Nie Zhe's followers.

24:31.220 --> 24:32.700
With you poisoned,

24:33.140 --> 24:34.570
unable to attend to greater matters,

24:35.530 --> 24:36.730
those remnants

24:36.730 --> 24:38.490
would surely reveal themselves.

24:38.490 --> 24:40.420
Then you cleanse them in blood.

24:40.420 --> 24:41.530
Two birds with one arrow.

24:41.530 --> 24:42.860
Truly an excellent scheme.

24:42.860 --> 24:44.250
Zhao...

24:46.620 --> 24:47.460
Zhao!

24:49.330 --> 24:50.900
I just wanted you to stay.

24:53.490 --> 24:54.570
This is Li Sect.

24:54.570 --> 24:55.570
(Carefree)

24:55.570 --> 24:56.810
Do you think you can leave

24:57.860 --> 24:59.330
without my permission?

25:01.220 --> 25:02.140
Mu Qingyan,

25:03.570 --> 25:04.660
why must it be like this?

25:05.290 --> 25:07.140
We had this journey

25:07.140 --> 25:08.290
only by fate.

25:09.330 --> 25:10.940
Now that fate has ended,

25:11.900 --> 25:13.220
it's time to part peacefully.

25:13.220 --> 25:14.330
That's nonsense.

25:15.490 --> 25:17.220
You're just timid,

25:17.220 --> 25:18.330
afraid of being blamed.

25:20.633 --> 25:22.939
Have you forgotten what we saw
in the underground palace?

25:23.620 --> 25:26.140
Mu Donglie and Luo Shiyun
could overcome countless hardships.

25:26.140 --> 25:27.050
So can we.

25:27.570 --> 25:29.220
Mu Qingyan, wake up.

25:29.220 --> 25:30.530
With Mu Donglie's power,

25:30.530 --> 25:31.770
even he could not openly

25:31.770 --> 25:33.380
marry Luo Shiyun.

25:33.380 --> 25:34.906
He either hid in an underground palace

25:34.917 --> 25:35.700
or fled far away.

25:36.330 --> 25:37.730
Let alone you and me.

25:38.180 --> 25:39.660
What could we possibly do?

25:40.730 --> 25:42.420
The demonic sect

25:42.420 --> 25:43.270
and the Six Sects

25:43.280 --> 25:44.530
are irreconcilable enemies.

25:44.530 --> 25:46.220
I cannot abandon my family

25:46.220 --> 25:47.620
and duties for you.

25:47.620 --> 25:49.140
I'd never do that for anyone!

25:49.570 --> 25:50.410
You can't leave!

25:54.810 --> 25:56.660
If you insist on keeping me...

25:58.180 --> 26:00.860
This blade has taken many lives.

26:01.770 --> 26:04.290
I won't disgrace my aunt's name.

26:07.050 --> 26:08.250
You want to kill me?

26:26.900 --> 26:27.900
Let me go.

26:36.860 --> 26:38.216
Young Master, bad news!

26:38.227 --> 26:39.460
(Carefree)
Nie Zhe was rescued.

26:43.810 --> 26:44.730
Miss Cai,

26:44.730 --> 26:46.180
that isn't how to hold a blade.

26:46.180 --> 26:47.140
It's so frightening.

26:49.330 --> 26:50.170
Speak.

26:53.010 --> 26:53.850
Young Master,

26:54.140 --> 26:55.940
a man in black
just broke into the dungeon,

26:55.940 --> 26:57.250
injured Shisan, rescued Nie Zhe,

26:57.250 --> 26:58.090
and...

26:59.380 --> 27:00.730
killed Lady Sun.

27:22.700 --> 27:23.540
You may go.

27:24.290 --> 27:25.130
Catch them first.

27:25.380 --> 27:27.420
No need for you
to trouble yourself with that.

27:27.420 --> 27:29.220
Were you not ready to leave just now?

27:29.770 --> 27:31.530
The one who killed Uncle Chang

27:32.980 --> 27:34.220
must be dealt with.

27:34.220 --> 27:36.090
You can stay for one day.

27:36.940 --> 27:38.730
But what about a month? A year?

27:38.730 --> 27:39.940
You come

27:39.940 --> 27:41.010
and go as you please.

27:42.810 --> 27:44.090
What do you take Li Sect for?

27:45.050 --> 27:46.420
If you wish to stay,

27:47.900 --> 27:49.570
you may never leave.

27:50.530 --> 27:51.649
Have you thought it through?

28:09.660 --> 28:10.500
Miss Cai...

29:32.049 --> 29:33.606
The strike pierced the Baihui acupoint.

29:33.617 --> 29:34.467
Death was instant.

29:35.090 --> 29:36.276
There should've been no pain.

29:36.860 --> 29:38.380
We've searched everywhere.

29:38.563 --> 29:40.530
There is no trace of Nie Zhe
or the man in black.

29:40.530 --> 29:41.370
Could it be

29:42.079 --> 29:43.330
that there is a secret passage?

29:43.330 --> 29:45.130
The Nie clan controlled
the sect for decades.

29:45.730 --> 29:47.110
A cunning rabbit has three burrows.

29:47.860 --> 29:49.506
A secret passage
would not be surprising.

29:49.940 --> 29:51.180
But this man in black

29:51.900 --> 29:54.180
knows the Nie clan's secrets so well.

29:58.313 --> 30:00.266
Bury her according to the rites
of a chief's wife

30:01.380 --> 30:02.490
with full honors.

30:02.810 --> 30:03.730
Young Master...

30:03.730 --> 30:04.570
All of you, leave.

30:09.770 --> 30:10.610
Yes.

30:17.880 --> 30:19.400
The Young Master seems in low spirits.

30:21.660 --> 30:22.660
If only Miss Cai

30:23.010 --> 30:23.850
were here.

31:21.420 --> 31:22.260
Zhao!

31:23.220 --> 31:24.060
Master.

31:26.490 --> 31:28.250
We truly share a bond.

31:28.598 --> 31:29.968
I've been thinking of you for days.

31:29.979 --> 31:30.979
And you came to fetch me.

31:31.380 --> 31:32.220
Come on.

31:32.810 --> 31:33.650
Were you injured?

31:34.700 --> 31:35.540
Good to hear.

31:43.050 --> 31:44.010
The priority now

31:44.010 --> 31:45.330
is to find the man in black,

31:45.330 --> 31:46.250
avenge Uncle Chang,

31:47.180 --> 31:48.860
and prevent further disaster.

31:49.860 --> 31:50.700
Zhao,

31:52.050 --> 31:54.700
do you truly believe
what Mu Qingyan says?

31:54.700 --> 31:56.700
If he could impersonate Chang Ning,

31:56.700 --> 31:59.010
why could he not fabricate
a man in black

31:59.010 --> 32:00.140
and stage a play for you?

32:00.940 --> 32:01.840
Master,

32:01.840 --> 32:03.490
I've fought that man in black.

32:03.490 --> 32:04.570
He is indeed unfathomable.

32:04.860 --> 32:06.220
By your account,

32:06.220 --> 32:08.140
among the Seven Star Elders,

32:08.140 --> 32:09.490
two still remain.

32:09.940 --> 32:10.850
It's possible

32:10.850 --> 32:12.860
that this man in black
is a hidden third elder.

32:14.570 --> 32:15.870
They're inexperienced and unaware

32:16.220 --> 32:17.596
of how cunning the demonic sect is.

32:17.810 --> 32:18.643
Mu Qingyan,

32:18.654 --> 32:20.250
as the Young Master
of the demonic sect,

32:20.250 --> 32:22.980
disguised himself as Chang Ning
in Qingque Sect for months.

32:22.980 --> 32:25.140
Even I was deceived by him.

32:25.140 --> 32:28.250
One who possesses such scheming
is no ordinary person.

32:28.250 --> 32:30.220
Once a fraud, always a fraud.

32:30.220 --> 32:32.336
Yet you, for such a deceitful man,

32:32.347 --> 32:34.076
involved yourselves
in the internal strife.

32:34.087 --> 32:35.457
What do you take

32:35.560 --> 32:36.730
Qingque Sect,

32:37.420 --> 32:39.330
your own lives,

32:39.330 --> 32:41.290
and your loved ones for?

32:41.290 --> 32:42.130
Yunke.

32:43.940 --> 32:44.780
Yuzhi,

32:45.050 --> 32:45.940
Zhao,

32:45.940 --> 32:47.940
you two snuck away this time.

32:47.940 --> 32:50.149
Your master was worried sick.

32:50.160 --> 32:51.140
If I hadn't stopped him,

32:51.151 --> 32:52.660
he'd have ridden into the Youming Path

32:52.660 --> 32:53.500
to rescue you.

32:56.330 --> 32:58.140
We even had to find ways

32:58.140 --> 32:59.660
to protect your reputations.

32:59.660 --> 33:00.873
There must not be a next time.

33:01.380 --> 33:02.860
It was my fault.

33:05.050 --> 33:06.940
I won't make you worry again.

33:16.140 --> 33:17.420
Milady,

33:17.420 --> 33:18.940
you are finally back.

33:18.940 --> 33:20.290
Was the trip smooth?

33:20.290 --> 33:21.620
Did anything interesting happen?

33:23.010 --> 33:23.850
Nothing.

33:26.620 --> 33:28.250
Are you hungry?

33:28.250 --> 33:29.420
Would you like some wonton?

33:29.420 --> 33:30.940
When I heard you were returning,

33:30.940 --> 33:32.140
I learned how to make them.

33:32.140 --> 33:33.826
I even prepared
the front of the pork leg.

33:36.090 --> 33:36.940
The wonton is here.

34:18.707 --> 34:20.787
Mu Qingyan, as the Young Master
of the demonic sect,

34:21.050 --> 34:22.460
disguised himself as Chang Ning

34:22.470 --> 34:24.420
in Qingque Sect for months.

34:24.420 --> 34:25.650
Once a fraud,

34:25.650 --> 34:26.610
always a fraud.

34:27.130 --> 34:29.740
Yet you, for such a deceitful man,

34:29.740 --> 34:31.480
involved yourselves
in the internal strife.

34:32.130 --> 34:33.130
What do you take

34:33.980 --> 34:35.010
Qingque Sect,

34:35.610 --> 34:36.980
your own lives,

34:37.740 --> 34:39.210
and your loved ones for?

35:01.650 --> 35:02.490
Milady.

35:04.940 --> 35:05.780
Milady?

35:19.780 --> 35:21.260
I'll never eat wonton again.

35:21.940 --> 35:23.170
Don't mention wonton again.

36:45.400 --> 36:56.060
=Generation to Generation=

37:14.820 --> 37:19.230
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

37:19.795 --> 37:24.410
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

37:24.750 --> 37:29.315
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

37:29.840 --> 37:34.140
♪Free to wander in the world♪

37:37.085 --> 37:41.785
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

37:42.310 --> 37:46.600
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

37:47.260 --> 37:51.290
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

37:51.605 --> 37:56.730
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

37:57.305 --> 38:02.115
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

38:02.330 --> 38:06.500
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

38:07.225 --> 38:11.160
♪I freely roam in the world♪

38:11.660 --> 38:16.935
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

38:39.665 --> 38:44.795
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

38:45.160 --> 38:49.530
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

38:49.795 --> 38:53.925
♪I freely roam in the world♪

38:54.110 --> 38:59.685
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
